subtitleNullable: Data about the cars on second market in Moldova till 2021 year
descriptionNullable:
Data about the cars on second market in Moldova till 2021 year

The data set is the statistics of car parameters in the secondary market in Moldova.

The set includes a number of categorical and numerical values ​​that make up one entry (line). The number of records can be found as the number of lines.

Each column in the record is a separate parameter.

Among these parameters are the target for the prediction problem (regression) - the price of the car.

Also among the parameters there is a target for the task of classification - the type of transmission.

The last task can be considered, for example, as an example of the task of filling out passes (if the seller has not indicated the corresponding parameter).
